  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK326">
<l>kollāmai mēlkoṇ ṭoḻukuvāṉ vāḻnāḷmēṟ</l>
<l>cellā tuyiruṇṇuṅ kūṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Yama, the destroyer of life, will not attack the life of him, who acts under the determination of never destroying life.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
